title: Ep 97: Bouba or Kiki
description:
In This Episode: We open the episode up with a listener review, a husband follows his dream but forgot to tell his wife, a fiancé  has an insane demand from his soon to be wife, a listener shares a horrifying story about being alone in the woods, and this ex-girlfriend realizes she forgot some shit at her boyfriends apartment. For this week's Circle Jerdge Christian is here to give the definitive answer on what items are giving Bouba or Kiki.
